Package com.nestedbird.modules.formparser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FormField
    This class processes the name of a Form Field For example, if a form field has the name of "sausage", then it is referencing the field sausage.
    FormParse
    This class processes the payload of a form and saves the data to the database Because different variable types may be processed differently, this class supports methods for handling all sorts of different datatypes and situations.
    ParameterMapParser
    The ParameterMapParser processes the payload from a form submission.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FormFieldType
    Enumeration of different possible FormFieldTypes as used by FormField
